  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose is to study natural process of gallstones in common bile duct, stones less than
      or equal to 6 mm. And if the gallstones give any complications under 1 year follow up. The
      second outcome is to study side-effects of gallstones removed with surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
