  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  cholecystectomy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Ongoing icterus or pancreatitis

          -  History of anamneses pancreatitis/icterus

          -  Allergy against x-ray contrast

          -  Stones more than 6 mm in ductus

          -  No passage of contrast to duodenum

          -  malignant
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
